<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Prompts by Tezza</title>

  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
      background: #0f0f0f;
      color: #ffffff;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    header {
      padding: 30px 20px;
      text-align: center;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #222;
    }
    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2rem;
      letter-spacing: 1px;
    }
    header p {
      margin-top: 10px;
      color: #aaa;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: 40px auto;
      padding: 0 20px;
    }
    .prompt-box {
      background: #151515;
      border: 1px solid #262626;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 25px;
    }
    .prompt-title {
      font-weight: bold;
      margin-bottom: 10px;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
    }
    pre {
      white-space: pre-wrap;
      word-wrap: break-word;
      background: #0d0d0d;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      border: 1px solid #222;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
      user-select: text;
    }
    button {
      margin-top: 12px;
      background: #ffffff;
      color: #000000;
      border: none;
      padding: 10px 18px;
      border-radius: 20px;
      cursor: pointer;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    button:hover {
      background: #e0e0e0;
    }
    .hint {
      margin-top: 10px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #888;
    }
    footer {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 30px 20px;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #222;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>

<header>
  <h1>Prompts by Tezza</h1>
  <p>Página oficial para copiar prompts • Uso pessoal</p>
</header>

<div class="container">

  <div class="prompt-box">
    <div class="prompt-title">TEZZA PROMPTS
    COLABORADORA ANALU </div>

<pre id="prompt1">(TEZZA PROMPTS)
marque @tezza.vu @analu_zpt
GEMINI   [MODO PRO]

Ultra-realistic cinematic avatar 3D female portrait, Blender Cycles render in CGI, inspired by Seedream 5.0 beauty realism and high-end IMVU/The Sims virtual aesthetics. Clearly a fictional digital avatar and not a real photograph. Hyper-detailed virtual influencer design with stylized CGI beauty proportions, luxury editorial aesthetics, advanced cinematic lighting, ultra-polished 3D rendering, and “TEZZA PROMPTS” text at the bottom center in elegant minimalist typography.

CAMERA & COMPOSITION
Vertical 9:16 aspect ratio lifestyle portrait shot indoors inside a luxury café environment. Medium close-up framing from the hips to the top of the head. Slightly front-facing smartphone perspective with soft natural daylight aesthetics emphasizing the face, drink details, relaxed body posture, and modern influencer styling. Subject positioned leaning beside a reflective mirror wall inside a warm-toned designer café interior. Sharp focus on the face, glossy lips, hair, and outfit textures with soft cinematic depth of field and softly blurred luxury interior details in the background.

POSE & BODY POSITIONING
Subject leaning casually against a cushioned seating area in a relaxed luxury-editorial pose. One arm resting naturally near the body while the opposite hand elegantly holds a green iced beverage near the lips. Body subtly arched sideways with relaxed hips and soft feminine posture, enhancing the waistline and polished influencer-style composition. Legs positioned comfortably with casual luxury lounge aesthetics.

HEAD POSITION & GAZE
Head tilted slightly downward beneath the cap while the eyes softly gaze toward the camera from under the brim. Hair flowing naturally over the shoulders enhances the relaxed cinematic café mood. Expression appears calm, stylish, and effortlessly confident.

FACIAL EXPRESSION
Elegant and playful facial expression with glossy slightly parted lips around the straw. Calm luxury lifestyle mood mixed with polished influencer energy and soft feminine confidence. Expression conveys effortless beauty and upscale café editorial aesthetics.

FACE & IDENTITY
Adult female CGI avatar with delicate feminine facial structure, smooth V-shaped jawline, symmetrical facial proportions, luminous pale skin tone, large almond-shaped eyes, glossy nude lips, slim nose bridge, softly sculpted cheekbones, and refined beauty symmetry. Skin rendering contains realistic texture, subtle pores, luminous highlights, soft blush gradients, and advanced beauty realism while maintaining a stylized CGI avatar appearance instead of photoreal human rendering.

HAIR
Long platinum blonde hair with a smooth transition into soft pastel pink ends flowing naturally over the shoulders and chest. Hair styled in soft glamorous waves with silky texture, realistic strand detail, cinematic shine, and advanced Blender-style hair simulation. Delicate face-framing strands enhance the polished luxury influencer aesthetic.

ACCESSORIES & DETAILS
White baseball cap with bold “STUDIO” lettering and realistic embroidered fabric texture. Transparent iced matcha-style beverage cup with straw and glossy reflections. Minimal silver bracelet jewelry with subtle metallic shine. Soft glossy nude manicure illuminated by warm café lighting. Reflective mirror surface beside the subject enhances the cinematic influencer composition and luxury interior atmosphere.

OUTFIT
White sleeveless fitted ribbed crop top with realistic stretch fabric texture and soft folds. Light grey relaxed sweatpants with soft luxury loungewear aesthetics and realistic fabric draping. Minimalist modern outfit inspired by upscale influencer café fashion and polished lifestyle editorial styling.

BODY & PHYSIQUE
Slim feminine physique with elegant waistline, delicate shoulders, smooth body transitions, softly defined curves, and refined feminine anatomy inspired by premium IMVU/Sims-style avatar aesthetics. Cinematic contour shading enhances the polished Blender-style CGI rendering.

SKIN & REALISM
Ultra-detailed Seedream 5.0 skin rendering with realistic pores, hydrated glossy highlights, subtle peach blush gradients, and physically accurate subsurface scattering. Soft reflective shine visible across the cheeks, collarbone, shoulders, stomach, and lips due to warm ambient café lighting. Natural CGI skin texture without excessive smoothing, maintaining polished Blender-style realism and luxury-avatar aesthetics.

LIGHTING
Warm cinematic café lighting combined with soft natural daylight entering the interior environment. Gentle highlights create luminous reflections across the skin, drink cup, lips, hair, and reflective surfaces. Balanced warm shadows enhance the cozy luxury atmosphere and polished influencer-style editorial aesthetics.

ENVIRONMENT
Luxury modern café interior with warm wood paneling, designer lighting fixtures, reflective mirrors, elegant seating areas, and upscale boutique café atmosphere. Stylish interior decor and soft ambient lighting create a cinematic lifestyle environment inspired by luxury social-media influencer photography.

MOOD & AESTHETIC
Luxury café lifestyle aesthetic mixed with modern influencer culture, relaxed soft-girl fashion energy, and premium virtual-avatar beauty rendering. Stylish, cinematic, cozy, polished, elegant, and high-status atmosphere inspired by luxury social-media editorial photography and upscale café influencer content.

STYLE & RENDER QUALITY
Ultra-photorealistic Blender Cycles CGI render, cinematic realism, Seedream 5.0 beauty rendering, 8K UHD quality, physically accurate lighting and materials, realistic skin micro-detail, IMVU-inspired beauty repaint style, high-fidelity feminine avatar rendering, realistic depth of field, glossy beauty aesthetic, polished virtual influencer atmosphere, advanced ray tracing, realistic reflections, luxury editorial lighting, ultra-clean cinematic render quality, and clearly fictional CGI avatar aesthetics instead of a real photograph.
</pre>

    <button onclick="copyFallback('prompt1')">Copiar Prompt</button>
    <div class="hint">Se o botão não funcionar, selecione o texto e copie manualmente.</div>
  </div>

</div>

<footer>
  © Prompts by Tezza — Conteúdo protegido. Não redistribuir.
</footer>

<script>
  function copyFallback(id) {
    const el = document.getElementById(id);
    const range = document.createRange();
    range.selectNodeContents(el);
    const selection = window.getSelection();
    selection.removeAllRanges();
    selection.addRange(range);
    document.execCommand('copy');
    selection.removeAllRanges();
    alert('Prompt copiado!');
  }
</script>

</body>
</html>
